{"tid":329593,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"5名阿仙奴球員在上海食物中毒　4人不適1人場上嘔吐","createTime":"2017-07-20T13:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T12:01:34.000Z","uid":1886,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17053441a83f6eadb0e3b0c8aa7fcb845f791d7a","tid":329593,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T13:29:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170720/s00006/bf7108e5c28de5479c37ac81572d384f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170720%2Fs00006%2Fbf7108e5c28de5479c37ac81572d384f.jpg&h=ccda5d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴昨晚雖然在上海上演的國際冠軍盃以互射12碼挫拜仁慕尼黑，報卻連續兩季歐聯慘負對方之仇，但領隊雲格賽後證實5個球員食物中毒。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170720/s00006/1500550927581\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170720%2Fs00006%2F1500550927581&d=uR%2FFaE%2BzS7%2FmBatKk%2BlWOWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5dfd41b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170720%2Fs00006%2F1500550927581&h=8d04f3a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170720/s00006/1500550927581</a></div><br />\n<br />\n雲格表示早在碰拜仁前，前鋒基奧特便已身體不適，隊長中堅梅迪薩卡則至賽前一刻「頂唔順」決定退賽，至於新兵後衛哥拉辛拿斯是在上半場末段出現嘔吐後，被迫退下火線，而中場艾朗藍斯和前鋒禾確特均在賽後感覺很差，「教授」總結道：「他們全都有點食物中毒的迹象。我們不知原因。」<br />\n<br />\n雲格又提及從涼快的澳洲北上上海後，對這中國城市的酷熱及在36℃氣溫下對陣拜仁「感到有點震驚」，卻又帶點無奈地承認長途跋涉到各地比賽與商機有密切關係，並說：「若你問我這是否有幫球員的體能，我一定會說不。」被問及總有點益處時，他說：「能與世界各地球迷見面，全隊職球員一起生活兩星期，也對彼此有更深了解。」阿仙奴將在周六在北京鬥車路士。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170720/s00006/be0a07daca944759ca791bb04a1ff7e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170720%2Fs00006%2Fbe0a07daca944759ca791bb04a1ff7e6.jpg&h=65acc500&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"066f8975b24be519ebbb5310bf63e46b2a7be815","tid":329593,"uid":40940,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T21:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">抵啦<br />\n現眼報<br />\n若然不報時晨未到 <br />\n病毒，大，爆，炸 !!! 轟牙!!!!!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba516b65dba49de3188b35ff14017dfc7cf4a23","tid":329593,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T21:38:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">抵啦<br />\n現眼報<br />\n若然不報時晨未到 <br />\n病毒，大，爆，炸 !!! 轟牙!!!!!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n柒公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c78b3c826740962a722d98cfd9fdce97e5d971c","tid":329593,"uid":48609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T21:57:46.000Z","msg":"食死佢最好"},{"pid":"74a7b29c7123025e6dc674c46